summary: i'm so glad i'm not the only one who thinks niko's treatment of eve is a lot of bs. he's just that kind of person who's...
question: i'm so glad i'm not the only one who thinks niko's treatment of eve is a lot of bs. he's just that kind of person who's conflict-avoidant to the point of not resolving ANY tension whatsoever, even when eve repeatedly asks him to speak his mind, he says it's all fine, and is just passive-aggressive instead and expecting her to figure it out on her own until he reaches his boiling point, so i think eve is just trying avoid that tension in the first place by hiding more and more of herself.
answer: OMG, yes. most of people see him just like the perfect husband who just wants to protect his wife but there’s so much more behind this and I’m glad I’m not the only one who saw this.
